---
import StaticLayout from '../layouts/StaticLayout.astro';
---

<StaticLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="FreeToolStack privacy policy. Learn how we handle your data.">
  <p><em>Last updated: March 2026</em></p>

  <h2>The Short Version</h2>
  <p>
    Your files never leave your device. Our tools process everything in your browser.
    We don't collect, store, or transmit your file data.
  </p>

  <h2>What We Collect</h2>
  <p>We collect minimal data to operate the website:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Analytics data</strong>: Anonymous page views and tool usage counts (via Google Analytics 4). No personal data is linked to these events.</li>
    <li><strong>IP addresses</strong>: Temporarily logged by our web server for security purposes. These are not stored long-term.</li>
    <li><strong>Cookies</strong>: We use essential cookies for site functionality and analytics cookies with your consent.</li>
    <li><strong>Email</strong>: If you voluntarily subscribe to our newsletter, we store your email address. You can unsubscribe at any time.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>What We Don't Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>File contents (all processing happens in your browser)</li>
    <li>Personal information beyond what you voluntarily provide</li>
    <li>Keystroke data or form inputs from tool usage</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Cloudflare</strong>: Hosting and CDN</li>
    <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong>: Anonymous usage analytics</li>
    <li><strong>Ad networks</strong>: Display advertising (configurable, respects ad blockers)</li>
    <li><strong>Stripe</strong>: Payment processing for premium subscriptions</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Your Rights (GDPR/CCPA)</h2>
  <p>
    You have the right to access, correct, or delete any personal data we hold about you.
    Since we collect minimal data, this primarily applies to newsletter subscriptions.
    Contact us at <strong>hello@freetoolstack.com</strong> to exercise these rights.
  </p>

  <h2>Changes</h2>
  <p>We may update this policy from time to time. Significant changes will be announced on our website.</p>
</StaticLayout>
